check_hyperoo_backup : a vbs script to monitor your hyperoo backup (www.hyperoo.net)

Usage: check_hyperoo /backup:<value> /warning:<value> /critical:<value>

/backup                       Name Of the Backup (Case sensitive)
/warning                      Number of hours since last backup (Warn)
/critical                     Number of hours since last backup (Crit)

Exemple :

C:\Program Files\NSClient++>cscript scripts\check_hyperoo.vbs /backup:"Hyperv-2 Journalier" /warning:10 /critical:15

OK: backup Hyperv-2 Journalier is OK
